title: Bas - Last Winter (2014) - 320kbps
description:
Last Winter is the debut studio album by American rapper Bas and was released on April 29, 2014 by Dreamville Records and Interscope Records. It includes features from J. Cole, K-Quick, Irvin Washington, and Mack Wilds.[1] The album debuted at 103 on the Billboard 200 with 3,601 copies sold in its first week.[2]
